# Privacy Policy for ST Wallpapers 4k

Effective Date: 12 December 2025

we operates the ST Wallpapers 4k mobile application.

This page informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of information when you use our App.

### 1. Information We Do NOT Collect
We do not collect any personal information from users of our App. The App provides wallpapers and does not require users to create an account, sign in, or provide any personal data.

We do not collect, store, or share:
- Name, email address, phone number
- Location data
- Device ID or advertising ID
- Photos or photos from your gallery
- Any other personally identifiable information

### 2. Permissions
The App may request the following permissions:
- Internet access → Only to load wallpapers and show ads (if any)
- Set wallpaper → To apply wallpapers on your device
- Storage/Photos → Only to save downloaded wallpapers (Android 10+ ke baad scoped storage hai, user control mein rehta hai)

These permissions are used only for the core functionality of the app and no data is sent to our servers.

### 3. Third-Party Services
- The App uses Google AdMob (or whichever ad network you use) to display ads. AdMob may collect anonymized data for showing ads as per Google’s privacy policy:  
  https://policies.google.com/privacy

- We use Firebase Analytics/Crashlytics (if you use) only for crash reports and anonymous usage stats. No personal data is collected.

### 4. Children’s Privacy
Our App is suitable for all ages and does not knowingly collect any personal information from children under 13.

### 5. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy in the app and updating the "Effective Date" above.

### 6. Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, feel free to contact us at:  
prathameshkharode005@gmail.com

